videos.description: After being ejected against the Rockets, Clippers coach Doc Rivers says his son Austin Rivers was right to ask the refs to give him a technical foul.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Doc Rivers approves son Austin calling for his ejection) 2019/11/13

videos.headline: Doc Rivers approves son Austin calling for his ejection

videos.description: Austin Rivers says he enjoyed calling for his dad's technical foul and says he doubts he and Doc Rivers will go to dinner anytime soon.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Rivers on dad’s technical: ‘Doc's gotta keep his cool’) 2019/11/13

videos.headline: Rivers on dad's technical: 'Doc's gotta keep his cool'
